00:29:45.590 --> 00:29:46.690
Saya dah jadi lebih tinggi, kan?

00:29:47.260 --> 00:29:48.260
Hei!

00:29:49.030 --> 00:29:51.390
Dapatkannya! Ayuh!

00:29:52.260 --> 00:29:55.930
- Awak faham tak? - Jun Kyung! Tengok ni!

00:29:56.130 --> 00:29:57.330
Saya tidak percaya ini.

00:29:57.870 --> 00:29:59.670
Banyak sangat ikan, tapi saya rasa tak dapat tangkap satu pun.

