Aduh, macam mana kau boleh terlepas pandang tu? Seriuslah, macam mana kau tak perasan?

00:30:04.410 --> 00:30:05.410
Sejuk.

00:30:08.510 --> 00:30:09.610
Apa masalahnya?

00:30:14.520 --> 00:30:15.520
Do Hyun...

00:30:17.650 --> 00:30:20.660
Semakin aku nampak dia, semakin aku suka dia.

00:30:23.430 --> 00:30:24.990
